parameters:
General Garves: "Kukukuku! You took your sweet time, didn't you,
Ginga-kun?"
General Garves: "Because you were late, Pony-Ceres is..."
General Garves: "She ended up like this!!"
SV_ボイスのループ演奏 bgv_s1_020

General Garves: "I was waiting just to show you this girl's execution.
Be grateful!"
Ginga: "What execution! I won't let you do such a thing--!!"

General Garves: "Idiot, if she couldn't win against the opponent, what
makes you think you can do anything?"
General Garves: "Just sit there quietly and watch Pony-Ceres's end."
SV_ボイスのループ演奏 bgv_s1_020

General Garves: "Listen up, I'm going to send an electric shock right
into her head now."

General Garves: "Her brain will boil in an instant, and Pony-Ceres
will be off to the other world, that's the deal."

General Garves: "But no, I won't let her die that easily. She defied
Lord Dargnoa, she'll taste a hell more painful than death."

General Garves: "I'll fry her brain with just enough electricity so
she won't die. It's tricky to get it right, but if successful, she'll
join the ranks of the vegetative."

General Garves: "Kukukuku, it's more painful than death. She'll be a
living disgrace exposed for all to see!"

General Garves: "Well, how about it? Interesting way of execution,
isn't it?"

General Garves: "I'm excited to see what kind of face she'll make when
her brain burns."
General Garves: "You can do nothing but watch her end right there!!"
General Garves: "Now, let the execution begin!"
General Garves: "Burn the last moments of Pony-Ceres into your eyes!!"

The pitiful sight of Pony-Ceres defeated by Garves adorned the front
page of the newspaper.
Her brain fried, Pony-Ceres was reduced to a vegetative state.

Seeing her unable to fight after being violated by Zydarg, the people
despaired.
Afterwards, Japan fell under Zydarg's control in just a few days--
